<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>师生科学素质展示平台</title>
    <link rel="Shortcut Icon" href="./image/icon.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/core/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/core/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/core/select-panel.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/core/combo.select.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/module/index.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray">
    <header class="header">
        <h1 class="container header-logo">
            <img src="./image/logo.svg" alt="师生科学素质展示平台" width="273" height="48" class="header-logoImg">
        </h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container content">
        <section class="tip">
            <i class="icon icon-prompt"></i>
            如果未找到所属机构或相关信息，请联系上级管理员处理
        </section>
        <form class="sso-form-box" id="ssoForm">
            <dl class="form-box">
                <li class="form-item">
                    <dt class="form-item__label">区域</dt>
                    <dd class="form-item__content">
                        <div class="form-item-select select-panel-box" id="region">
                            <input type="text" class="form-input__inner" placeholder="请选择所在地" readonly>
                            <input type="hidden" name="provinceId" value="">
                            <input type="hidden" name="cityId" value="">
                            <input type="hidden" name="areaId" value="">
                        </div>
                    </dd>
                </li>
                <li class="form-item" required id="sso-form-school">
                    <dt class="form-item__label">学校</dt>
                    <dd class="form-item__content">
                        <select id="select-school" name="schoolId">
                            <option value="">请选择您的学校</option>
                        </select>
                    </dd>
                </li>
                <li class="form-item" required id="sso-form-class">
                    <dt class="form-item__label">班级</dt>
                    <dd class="form-item__content">
                        <select id="select-class" name="classId">
                            <option value="">请选择您的班级</option>
                        </select>
                    </dd>
                </li>
            </dl>
            <input class="form-button--default submit" type="submit" value="立即创建">
        </form>
        <div class="loading"></div>
    </div>
</body>
<script src="./js/lib/jquery-2.2.4.min.js"></script>
<script src="./js/lib/jquery.validate.min.js"></script>
<script src="./js/lib/jquery.combo.select.js"></script>
<script src="./js/core/config.js"></script>
<script src="./js/core/common.js"></script>
<script src="./js/core/select-panel.js"></script>
<script src="./js/module/index.js"></script>
</html>